------------- DNSCONTROL

  sudo addzone		- Add Zone to Bind
  sudo deletezone 	- Delete Zone from Bind
  sudo editzone   	- Edit a existing Zone
  sudo reloaddns  	- Reload All DNS Servers
  sudo reloadzone 	- Reload a Zone on All DNS Servers
  sudo dnssync		- Resend Slaves Configurations on All Slaves Servers

